META.prose: All of the state’s approximately 1,240 public school districts and 890 accredited private schools report student vaccine exemptions to the Department of State Health Services annually. A student receiving an exemption doesn’t necessarily indicate that student’s vaccination status. Find your school district below to see the number of exemptions for the 2013-2014 school year.
